# Zappafied

Zappafied is a powerful, browser-based tool designed to transform your vocal audio recordings into interactive musical scores. By analyzing uploaded vocal tracks, Zappafied extracts notes and rhythms, allowing users to visualize and play alongside the generated MIDI sequences. Whether you're a musician looking to transcribe vocals, a music educator aiming to demonstrate pitch and rhythm, or an enthusiast eager to explore audio analysis, Zappafied offers an intuitive and seamless experience.

